        {
            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "Also happening to me whenever I try to open ~/.bashrc file, works well otherwise, apparently.\r\n\r\nNvim execute from bash of Pop!_OS having the following version:\r\n```bash\r\nnvim -v\r\nNVIM v0.11.0-dev\r\nBuild type: RelWithDebInfo\r\nLuaJIT 2.1.0-beta3\r\n```\r\nIt seems to me that the problem is caused by `noice` plugin since the problem is solved if all noice configuration is removed.",
